                  <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                    <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                      <span class="fraction_box ml_0"><span>1</span><span>2</span></span>과 
                      <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>4</span></span>의 크기를 비교해 보세요.
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </h3>
                <div class="compare_wrap">
                <span lang="y" class="f32b">두 분수의 크기가</span>
                <div class="dropdown_wrap">
                  <select class="custom_dropdown" data-answer-single="같습니다.">
                    <option value=""></option>
                    <option value="같습니다."></option>
                    <option value="다릅니다."></option>
                  </select>
                  </div>
                </div>
